---
import bgPattern from "@/assets/bg-pattern-hero-home.svg"
import talentImg from "@/assets/image-world-class-talent.jpg"
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
---

<section>
	<Image
		src={talentImg}
		alt="Person with hair in a bun wearing a white top and jeans, viewed from behind, looking at photos and notes pinned to a white wall"
	/>
	<div class="bg-[#FDF3F0] relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="relative z-10 px-6">
			<div class="flex flex-col items-center py-20">
				<h1 class="heading-1 text-center text-balance mb-6 text-primary">
					World-class talent
				</h1>
				<p class="text-center body-text mb-8">
					We are a crew of strategists, problem-solvers, and technologists.
					Every design is thoughtfully crafted from concept to launch, ensuring
					success in its given market. We are constantly updating our skills in
					a myriad of platforms.
				</p>
				<p class="text-center body-text">
					Our team is multi-disciplinary and we are not merely interested in
					form â€” content and meaning are just as important. We give great
					importance to craftsmanship, service, and prompt delivery. Clients
					have always been impressed with our high-quality outcomes that
					encapsulates their brand's story and mission.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<Image
			src={bgPattern}
			alt=""
			class="absolute -top-52 rotate-180 -right-12 opacity-35"
		/>
	</div>
</section>
